{"id":620943,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/【异闻观止】15岁少年多次浏览网上反华信息被批评/","date":"2019-10-29T05:21:00Z","modified":"2019-10-29T05:21:00Z","title":"【异闻观止】15岁少年多次浏览网上反华信息被批评教育","content":"<p>近日，双桥公安分局破获一起利用互联网多次浏览观看“反华”“仇华”信息的案件。</p>\n<p>经查，李某（男，15岁，承德市人）因受其他“精日”分子蛊惑登录“恶俗维基”，多次观看刻意歪曲中国历史，曲解国内外热点新闻、事件的信息。</p>\n<p>目前，李某被公安机关和所在学校严肃批评教育后已深刻认识到自己的错误。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EIBPbdAU4AMVBIl.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-620944\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EIBPbdAU4AMVBIl.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EIBPbdAU4AMVBIl.jpg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EIBPbdAU4AMVBIl-300x184.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"B7yqZulTrl\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/%e3%80%90%e5%bc%82%e9%97%bb%e8%a7%82%e6%ad%a2%e3%80%91%e6%9d%91%e6%b0%91%e5%be%ae%e4%bf%a1%e7%be%a4%e7%a7%b0%e5%8c%96%e8%82%a5%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e5%90%ab%e9%87%8f%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%9f-%e8%a2%ab%e5%86%85/\">【异闻观止】村民微信群称化肥公司含量不够 被内蒙古公安行拘</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【异闻观止】村民微信群称化肥公司含量不够 被内蒙古公安行拘》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/%e3%80%90%e5%bc%82%e9%97%bb%e8%a7%82%e6%ad%a2%e3%80%91%e6%9d%91%e6%b0%91%e5%be%ae%e4%bf%a1%e7%be%a4%e7%a7%b0%e5%8c%96%e8%82%a5%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e5%90%ab%e9%87%8f%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%9f-%e8%a2%ab%e5%86%85/embed/#?secret=B7yqZulTrl\" data-secret=\"B7yqZulTrl\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"VeIeSWkxQp\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/c